aspguidp.service.data.manager.impl

Class SimpleEntityDataManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • aspguidp.service.data.manager.impl.SimpleEntityDataManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AtomConsumer, AtomSupplier, DataManager, EntityDataManager

    public class SimpleEntityDataManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements EntityDataManager
    Basic implementation of the EntityDataManager interface which uses an EntityFactory instance to create Entity instances from given user input strings and string representations of atoms.
